name: Heart of Azeroth

main_spell_tooltip.description:
Create an Azerite beacon at a target location. After 2 sec, the Heart of Azeroth will relocate you to this beacon and deal 135 Fire damage to all nearby enemies.

For 10 sec after being relocated, you take 10% reduced damage.

passive_spell_tooltip.description:
Your movement speed is increased by 5%, and when you move more than 25 yds within 4 sec, gain 8 Strength for 20 sec.

This can only occur once every 30 sec.

Reduces the cooldown of Crusade by 10.0%, and increases your Versatility by 3.

When you activate Crusade, immediately heal for 5% of maximum health.

Your spells and abilities have a chance to strike your target for 115 Fire damage, and heal you for 50% of the damage dealt.

If your target is below 20% health, the chance for extra damage is increased by 400%.

Unique:  Corruption Resistance increased by 10.

Your spells and abilities have a high chance to impale your target with a spike of Azerite, causing 78 Fire damage.

When an Azerite spike deals damage, all damage you deal against that target is increased by 3% for 6 sec.
